Definition: the Muslim community or people, considered to extend from Mauritania to Pakistan
Example: moderate Muslims urge the Ummah to reject the terrorism of radical Muslims
Synonyms: Umma, Muslim_Ummah, Islamic_Ummah, Islam_Nation, community, noun, cognition, Islam, c, communication, plural, u, the, Muslim, or, people, considered, to, extend, from, Mauritania, Pakistan, moderate, Muslims, urge, reject, terrorism, of, radical
Category: noun.group
